He's willing to help with anything you ask.

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:33.639
Right?

00:07:35.519 --> 00:07:36.720
That depends on what it is.

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:41.399
Thank you, sir.

00:07:42.199 --> 00:07:43.000
How about this, sir.

00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:44.160
I'll

00:07:44.399 --> 00:07:45.000
